title.rendered: Can I Restore a File I Deleted Before I Download Dumpster?

content.rendered:
Yes, you can! With Deep Scan Recovery, you’ll be able to restore any photo, video, audio, or document file that was deleted before you downloaded Dumpster.

Find out more about Deep Scan Recovery here
